    "body": "Making this work with the `INotifyDeployComplete` interface that will be introduced with #13041 will be tricky.  Ideally we would just move `DoTransform` to `Transforms` and be done, but then `TransformOnCapture` messes that up by queuing `Transform` without having the `Transforms` trait to handle the callback.  This can be addressed in a future PR."
